muzhi

爬取数据

用python写了一个爬虫，在51job.com上爬去了和机器学习相关7500个职位，包括公司，职位，薪资基本信息，还有公司简介职位简介等信息。

switch_exp <- function(x){
if(x == "无工作经验")  x = "0"
else if(x == "2年经验") x = "2"
else if(x == "3-4年经验") x = "3-4"
else if(x == "1年经验") x= "1"
else if(x == "5-7年经验") x= "5-7"
else if(x == "") x = "NA"
else if(x == "8-9年经验" ) x = "8-9"
else if(x == "10年以上经验") x= "more than 10"

return(x)
}

exp <- sapply(df$req_exp, function(i)switch_exp(i))
names(exp) <- NULL
df$req_exp <- exp

switch_lev <- function(x){
if(x == "本科" )  x = "undergraduate"
else if(x ==  "硕士") x =  "matser"
else if(x == "博士") x = "PhD"
else x = "other"
return(x)
}

x$req.Lev[is.na(x$req.Lev)]<- '0'
x$req.Lev<- sapply(x$req.Lev, function(i)switch_lev(i))

ggplot(x) + geom_boxplot(aes(x = factor(req.Lev), y=income))

x$job_info_seg <- lapply(1:nrow(x),function(i){segment(x$job_info[i], work)})
job_word_top <- job_wf$job_word[order(job_wf$Freq, decreasing = T)[1:101]]
job_word_top <- job_word_top[-25]
job_word_top <- as.character(job_word_top)

做一个线性回归，选出对income贡献十分显著的工作描述关键字。

job_list <- lapply(x$job_info_seg ,function(i){as.numeric(job_word_top%in%i)})

t(matrix(unlist(job_list) ,nrow=100, ncol = nrow(x))) -> a
job_lm<- data.frame(income = x$income, mat = a)
lm <- lm(income~., data = job_lm)
p_value <- summary(lm)$coefficients[,4]

可以简单地认为这些关键词是我们找工作时的加分项

##选出p-value < 0.0005
job_word_top[p_value<0.0005]
